Text Color:

            h2, p { color: #ff00ff; }

Text Direction:

            h2, p { direction: rtl; }

Letter-spacing:

            h2, p { letter-spacing: 5px; }

text-transform:

 h2, p { text-transform: uppercase; }

White-span:

 h2, p { white-space: pre-wrap; }

Text-shadow:

 h2, p { text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px yellow; }

Word-spacing:

            h2, p { word-spacing: 5px; }

Text-indent:

            h2, p { text-indent: 2cm; }

Text-align:

            h2, p { text-align: center; }

Text-decoration:

            h2, p { text-decoration: inherit; }

Apply Texts in the below web page:
     
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>CSS texts Application</title>
        <style>
            h2, p { text-decoration: line-through; }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h2>The CSS Application Tutorial</h2>
        <p>Welcome to Software Developer tube channel, We look at the how CSS is used to style webpage.</p>
